  Finset.max' (Finset.filter (fun d => odd d) (Finset.divisors x)) ⟨1, Finset.mem_filter.mpr ⟨Finset.one_mem_divisors.mpr x.ne_zero, odd_one⟩⟩

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : 0 < x then
    Nat.find (Exists.intro (nat.find_greatest (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) (x + 1)) 
      (nat.find_spec (Exists.intro (nat.find_greatest (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) (x + 1)) 
        (nat.find_spec (Exists.intro (nat.find_greatest (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) (x + 1)) 
          (and.intro (nat.find_greatest_spec (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) (x + 1)).1 
            (and.intro (nat.find_greatest_spec (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) (x + 1)).2 
              (nat.find_greatest_le (fun d' => d' ∣ x ∧ d' % 2 = 1) (x + 1))))))))
  else 0

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  @Nat.find (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ Nat.Odd d ∧ ∀ d', d' ∣ x ∧ Nat.Odd d' → d' ≤ d) (Nat.find_spec (Nat.exists_odd_divisor x))
